						<p>On a Nandi-pillar standing opposite to the temple of Sōmēśvarasvāmin.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1439, Īśvara, Kārttīka, ba. 30, Friday, corresponding to 1517 A.D., November 13.</p>						

